      <abstract>
        <p>Howard Goldberg article on fifth edition of Frank E Johnson's Professional Wine Reference (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>Since 1977, retailers and sommeliers have answered customers' questions authoritatively by consulting Frank E. Johnson's omnibus Professional Wine Reference. It is published by Beverage Media Group of New York.</p>
        <p>The fifth edition of this alphabetized reference book, revised and updated, is a boon for novices and collectors. Its New York State entry adds a new region, Niagara Escarpment, a pinot noir zone.</p>
      </block>
